      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/22395"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Abner Benton House, built in 1819, earned a spot on the National Register of Historic Places in 1984.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxbow%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Oxbow lies 29 miles northeast of Watertown and 9 miles southwest of Gouverneur in northern Jefferson County.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        18
